      556.7,
      550.68,
      616.51
    ],
    "text": "Issued at 2.00 p.m. on 04 May 2026 The Intertropical Convergence Zone (ITCZ) is currently influencing the weather over the island. As a result, an increase in rainfall is expected over the island after 6 May.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota",
      "Iskoola Pota,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
