  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      620.42,
      550.77,
      696.29
    ],
    "text": "For tomorrow: Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in the Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, North-western, Uva and Eastern provinces and in Polonnaruwa, Galle, Matara and Mullaitivu districts after 2.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.119999885559082,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      698.81,
      550.77,
      731.33
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Galle and Matara districts.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      734.41,
      550.74,
      770.71
    ],
    "text": "Showers will occur in the Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Puttalam, Galle and Matara districts during the morning too.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      774.01,
      550.83,
      811.51
    ],
    "text": "Fairly strong winds of about (30-40) kmph can be expected at times over Northern and North-central provinces and in Hambantota district.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
